text: Centro Valle Intelvi is a comune in the Province of Como in the Lombardy region in Italy. It was created on 1 January 2018 from the former municipalities of Casasco d'Intelvi, Castiglione d'Intelvi and San Fedele Intelvi. == References == Category:2018 establishments in Italy Category:Settlements in Como
title: Centro Valle Intelvi
